    "updated_at": "2016-08-25T00:44:58Z",
    "body": "It is expected behavior when using `webFrame.setZoomFactor`, since it only changes current frame and current frame is gone after navigation.\n\nThe correct way is to use `webview.setZoomFactor`, which is supposed to keep the zoom factor through navigations. However when I just tried it I found the zoom factor still goes away after navigation, so this is a bug.\n"
