    "created_at": "2017-01-08T14:08:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-01-08T14:08:00Z",
    "body": "On my machine (win10, electron until 1.4.13), the main window's zoom factor will be reset when inserting new iframe element into the body by javascript."
  },
  {
