    "created_at": "2017-01-08T21:10:22Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-01-08T21:10:22Z",
    "body": "yes, but here's a simple work around. set the zoom with this:\r\n\r\n```\r\nwebFrame.setLayoutZoomLevelLimits(-999999, 999999);\r\nwebFrame.setZoomFactor(zoom);\r\nlet ezl = webFrame.getZoomLevel();\r\nwebFrame.setLayoutZoomLevelLimits(ezl, ezl);\r\n```"
  },
